        <div id="anatomy-card" class="card">
            <h2 class="question-text">Clue 2: Body Parts</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Look at a bat's wing and a human's arm. Even though they are used for different things (flying and grabbing), they have the same pattern of bones inside. This is a big clue that bats and humans might be related from a common ancestor!</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center my-4">
