        <!-- Resistance Card -->
        <div id="resistance-card" class="card">
            <h2 class="question-text">Clue 5: Resistance</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Sometimes, we use medicine or bug spray to get rid of germs or bugs. A few of them might survive because they are a little different. These survivors then have babies that are also resistant, and over time, the medicine or spray stops working. This is a fast example of evolution!</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center my-4">
